'''Adhiparasakthi Charitable, Medical, Educational and Cultural Trust''' ('''ACMEC''') is a charitable organization in [[Tamil Nadu]], [[India]].  It was founded in 1978 in [[Melmaruvathur]] by [[Bangaru Adigalar]]; it funds colleges and a hospital<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiaonapage.com/Sivaganga/Hospital/itemdetail-120573/SRI-ADHI-PARASAKTHI-HOSPITAL.htm|title=SRI ADHI PARASAKTHI HOSPITAL - Hospital - Sivaganga - IndiaOnAPage|website=www.indiaonapage.com|accessdate=3 October 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.punjabcolleges.com/31985-indiacolleges-Adhiparasakthi-Dental-College-and-Hospital-Melmaruvathur/|title=Adhiparasakthi Dental College and Hospital Melmaruvathur Tamil Nadu|website=www.punjabcolleges.com|accessdate=3 October 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cylex.in/company/sri-adhiparasakthi-hospital-10812283.html|title=Cylex Business Directory India|website=www.cylex.in|accessdate=3 October 2018}}</ref> as well as a variety of other local services.

